episodes.title: A Thundering
episodes.plot: Kayce settles into his new role at the ranch; A damaging article threatens to expose John; Rainwater pitches his new plan to the tribal council.

episodes.title: New Beginnings
episodes.plot: Kayce and Rip come to blows; Beth starts buying up land to protect the ranch; Monica begins a new chapter at the university.

episodes.title: The Reek of Desperation
episodes.plot: New powerful enemies look to block Rainwater and Jenkins' plans for a big business deal; John and Beth groom a new political candidate.

episodes.title: Only Devils Left
episodes.plot: John's enemies strike a direct hit on the Yellowstone. John forms an unlikely alliance. Kayce has his first day as a livestock officer.

episodes.title: Touching Your Enemy
episodes.plot: Jamie tries desperately to confront a previous mistake; Kayce tracks down evidence; Jimmy tries to make some extra cash on the side.

episodes.title: Blood the Boy
episodes.plot: Jamie makes a drastic move in order to protect his family; Jimmy takes a shot at a rodeo competition.

episodes.title: Resurrection Day
episodes.plot: Tensions escalate as the Beck brothers become frustrated by the Duttons' unwillingness to play ball; Jamie looks for a fresh start at the ranch.

episodes.title: Behind Us Only Grey
episodes.plot: John and Rip seek revenge; Monica ponders the consequences of her living situation on the ranch; Jimmy clears old debts.

episodes.title: Enemies by Monday
episodes.plot: The Duttons gear up for a final fight with the Becks; Beth helps Monica out of an uncomfortable situation.

episodes.title: Sins of the Father
episodes.plot: The feud with the Becks comes to a head as the Duttons scramble to save one of their own.
